in-ai-era-sparkles">Creative Writing in AI era :sparkles:</h2> <p>Time: Sunday Feb 1, 2025, 4:00-5:00pm</p> <h3 id="what-is-ai">What is AI?</h3> <p>It is like a growing word snake—each word stretches the story! Check the fun game out!</p> <p><a href="https://workshop-academy.github.io/blog/word_snake.html">AI in Word Snake Game</a></p> <p><a href="https://workshop-academy.github.io/blog/word_snake_v2.html">AI in Word Snake Game v2 (a little smarter version)</a></p> <h3 id="ai-rule">AI Rule:</h3> <ul> <li> Rule 1: Never use AI when it is not allowed — and definitely no cheating at school. </li> <li> Rule 2: Always think for yourself first. AI can help with ideas, but you make the final decisions. </li> <li> Rule 3: Keep personal information private. Do not share your full name, address, school, or phone number with AI. </li> <li> Rule 4: Ask an adult if something feels odd or confusing.** If AI says something strange or wrong, talk to a trusted grown‑up. </li> <li> Rule 5: Use AI kindly and responsibly. Don’t use AI to spread rumors, bully others, or create hurtful messages. </li> <li> Rule 6: Be curious, have fun, and stay safe. AI is a great helper when used wisely. </li> </ul> <h3 id="ai-and-creative-writing">AI and Creative Writing</h3> <p>Tell us about your experience! :smile:</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="links"/><category term="workshops"/><category term="links"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[creative writing in AI era]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Creative Writing Workshop (Beyong the Page)</title><link href="https://workshop-academy.github.io/blog/2025/workshop-creative-writing/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Creative Writing Workshop (Beyong the Page)"/><published>2025-02-20T18:30:16+00:00</published><updated>2025-02-20T18:30:16+00:00</updated><id>https://workshop-academy.github.io/blog/2025/workshop-creative-writing</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://workshop-academy.github.io/blog/2025/work